{"title":"钢板","authors":["王宝森"],"dates":[{"year":1982,"month":3,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢板"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江苏淮安　王宝森"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不埋怨经受淬火的痛苦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欣喜着强度、硬度的提高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在重锤下硬了骨、弯了腰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驮着重载让列车奔跑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"强硬、坚韧是钢板的特性，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有多的折磨才有多的创造，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"软骨病岂能南征北伐？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有韧性，就没有百折不挠！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"逾越重重险阻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忍受沉重疲劳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耗尽生命的力量"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向着遥远的目标……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}